      <blockquote class="text-xl font-medium text-white md:text-2xl">
        "TopGo has been essential to our rapid growth and ability to compete with established platforms. We can deploy new creator tools, chat features, and platform improvements instantly without interrupting any live streams. This agility has allowed us to respond to creator feedback immediately and stay ahead of the competition. It's been crucial to building trust with our creator community."
      </blockquote>
      <div class="mt-8">
        <div class="font-semibold text-purple-400">Alex Mitchell</div>
